reviewText: received as promised and in good condition
This series is absolutely  fantastic! Delivery is always timely and just as promised.
Very clever episodes here...I love the twists and turns within the storyline. good acting too. A must have for any collection!
I like that each eposide offers story lines that are enjoyable to watch . Each cast member gets a story and still enter act with each other.  I  also enjoyed # 14. Am waiting on # 15 and 16...
Great! Arrived early and we enjoyed watching it very much. Love the series. We have watched all of the series and really like all of them. Hope they make more.
